              works carefully and with due diligence.</p>

            <div class="icon-box d-flex position-relative" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
              <i class="bi bi-patch-check flex-shrink-0"></i>
              <div>
                <h4><a href="" class="stretched-link">Professional education</a></h4>
                <p>Our technicians have years of experience working at window manufacturing plants.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="icon-box d-flex position-relative" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
              <i class="bi bi-briefcase flex-shrink-0"></i>
              <div>
                <h4><a href="" class="stretched-link">Full toolkit</a></h4>
                <p>Technicians are equipped with everything needed to fix 90% of faults during a single visit.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="icon-box d-flex position-relative" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
              <i class="bi bi-shield-check flex-shrink-0"></i>
              <div>
                <h4><a href="" class="stretched-link">Safety</a></h4>
                <p>We use only certified parts and follow all safety procedures.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="icon-box d-flex position-relative" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
